{"tid":2402052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大肚婆被捕｜早產孕婦赴警總投訴 斥鄧炳強「作故仔」 區議員形容事件「人神共憤」","createTime":"2021-02-10T07:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T11:25:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":61,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"1ec9a4ad996de278c8dd492a6ca30cf50357ac54","tid":2402052,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:36:33.000Z","msg":"今日（10/2)劉女士與兩名區議員於警總前開記者會，交代投訴行動及嬰兒身體狀況。劉女士表示，難以感受警務署署長鄧炳強慰問的真誠，並不滿他否認涉事警務人員犯錯，以及指警員施以「最低武力」的說法。另外劉女士又質疑，自己今日才正式向警方投訴，但上月底鄧炳強卻指已接獲投訴，對警方所指的「投訴人」大感不解，有「作故仔」之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n記者會期間，劉女士數度哽咽，指兒子現時情況反覆，故仍非常憂慮。「之前醫院話佢有好轉，抆咗喉畀佢自己呼吸，但而家情況唔好又要再插喉......」劉女士一談到兒子便聲淚俱下，並表示希望今次正式投訴可為自己和兒子帶來公道，還大家清白，「希望可以公平、公正、公開調查，令我無罪」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210210/JIQG5G7XSNFRJDCDVYACQ7FP3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210210%2FJIQG5G7XSNFRJDCDVYACQ7FP3Q%2F&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=e53fee75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210210%2FJIQG5G7XSNFRJDCDVYACQ7FP3Q%2F&h=153a496f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210210/JIQG5G7XSNFRJDCDVYACQ7FP3Q/</a>"},{"pid":"af2fed428ec6dcf5df83dcf443ee0383d40dd3db","tid":2402052,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"死暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2514bea9414a18593d1e01946d77a1a8e2b89db7","tid":2402052,"uid":49329,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:46:12.000Z","msg":"咁呢位女士其他家人係咪依然支持黑警 ?"},{"pid":"9886d8276a19c803877c1b7859ac556f96b3f962","tid":2402052,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:49:29.000Z","msg":"專做傷天害理的事"},{"pid":"52377c35d8ec2bb0ff3ef2eaebb923e5418c00ea","tid":2402052,"uid":276191,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"2514bea9414a18593d1e01946d77a1a8e2b8